# Chat API Requests

### 1. Create a new chat session
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Conversation"
}

###

### 2. Send a message to the session (replace {sessionId} with the ID from step 1)
# @name sendMessage
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "how are you?"
}

###

### 3. Get all messages from the session
GET {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/messages
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get all sessions
GET {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Stream a message (real-time response)
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Tell me a short story"
}

###

### 6. Delete a session
DELETE {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}

###

### 7. Send a file with message (e.g., translate a PDF)
# Note: This is a multipart/form-data request
# You need to replace {sessionId} with an actual session ID
# You need to replace the file path with an actual file path
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/files
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Message"

Please translate this document to English
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./path/to/your/document.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### 8. Stream a file with message (real-time response)
# Note: This is a multipart/form-data request
# You need to replace {sessionId} with an actual session ID
# You need to replace the file path with an actual file path
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/files/stream
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Message"

Please summarize this document
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="document.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./path/to/your/document.txt
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--